            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div>
        
<p>The latest Steam Next Fest is in full swing, and there are hundreds of great demos for you to check out and play. </p>



<p>With so many demos, though, it can be hard to keep track and find the ones that stand out. That’s why we wanted to put together this list of all of the games that took part in May’s Insider Gaming Showcase that currently have demos available to play.</p>



<p>Before we get into it, be sure to download the free Insider Gaming App for the cleanest way to read your gaming news from&nbsp;<a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.insidergaming.app" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Google Play</a>&nbsp;or the&nbsp;<a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/insider-gaming/id6753984648" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">App Store</a>.</p>







<h2 id="h-insider-gaming-showcase-games-at-steam-next-fest">Insider Gaming Showcase Games At Steam Next Fest</h2>



<p>Steam Next Fest runs until June 22 and allows you to try out new and upcoming games. At the Insider Gaming Showcase, we featured 55 games that are looking for funding or publisher support. Of those 55 titles, 19 are available for you to try now.</p>



<p>So, check out the games, give them a shot, and be sure to wishlist to let the developers know you care! You can also check out the trailers for each game as well.</p>



